● Here's the lay of the land plus a plan. Quick context: you already have marketing tours at /tour (member) and /tour/admin —
  scroll-through pages with mock demos (lib/tourData.ts personas: Marcus/black, Jordan/blue, Sam/white) and CSS animations. They are
