  8. Follow graph — Follow button, followers/following lists (new this session)
  9. Private lessons — find an instructor, available slots, request, in-thread messaging, post-lesson review
  10. Journal — free-form + guided entries, private toggle, sharing an entry
  11. Events — public calendar + events near you
  12. Tournaments — browse/register, brackets, results, your competition history
  13. Challenge matches (new) — opt in, the profile Challenge button, propose/negotiate terms, waiver e-sign, live scoreboard,
  competition record
  14. Gallery — photos, tagging, hashtags, slideshow/layout modes
  15. Store — gear, cart, pay-at-pickup orders
  16. Notifications & Settings — push opt-in, check-in/feedback prompts, schedule & notification prefs, home gym, replay tour

  🏢 Gym admin / owner tour

  1. Admin dashboard — member/attendance counters, "Finish setting up" checklist
  2. Gym profile & settings — name/logo/description, review URL, feature toggles
  3. Members — roster, roles, belt verification & promotion, per-member class access
  4. View As — read-only impersonation of any member
  5. Classes — class wizard, programs/class groups, bulk day-of-week create, sessions
  6. Attendance reports — by class group / instructor / member
  7. Forum moderation — create/delete gym + group forums
  8. Invitations — individual link/QR + bulk CSV import
  9. Tournaments — create, divisions, registrations, brackets, run on the live console
  10. Challenge hosting — hosting opt-ins, visitor waivers, approve & run challenges
  11. Store management — products, order fulfillment (ready → picked up)
  12. Private-lesson / instructor oversight — instructor approvals
  13. Gym claiming + notifications

  🥋 Private instructor tour

